{
  "stem": "27543.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He saved my life twice, that he teach-- that I cooked for him, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was the person who I cooked when he invited the German soldiers there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a wonderful-- I told you, I never saw a German killing a Jew.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] excuse me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, by the beginning, at least 100 escaped to the parties as they thought if they escaped to the [? partisans ?], especially in Kremnitz and Ruhnu and [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "More than half escaped to the [? partisans. ?] And we didn't even see one come back alive.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- we-- we heard rumors that a lot of them escaped.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A lot of them, don't forget, was from the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They talked perfect Russian, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They thought that they escaped.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we never-- not one come back of those with over 100, not even one.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I tell you what we heard rumors.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The guards used to get letters that were just a card, we're fine, and hope you are fine.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] We didn't get no letters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had a postcard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We're fine.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Hope you are fine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We're fine.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's all.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Everything was printed, no writing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I never heard about the concentration camp along the war wasn't over.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, ma'am.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The forced labor-- I want to tell you one thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had plenty food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We worked for the [INAUDIBLE], for the Wehrmacht.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The German had the best food in the world.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You have no idea what food they had.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had everything, what they-- all from-- all from Holland, Belgium, Denmark, Yugoslavia, Hungary, from all over the world what they stoled, the Germans had the best food in the world.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They weren't hungry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had everything in the world.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Every night, they had six hot meals every week, except Saturday.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
